OL,3,CTOWIE star Jess Wright says son rushed
OL,4,Cto hospital after 'freak accident'
OL,6,FJess Wright has revealed her four-year-
OL,7,Fold son Presley was rushed to hospital
OL,8,Fby ambulance after he was "catapulted
OL,9,Foff a bouncy castle" at a birthday
OL,10,Fparty.
OL,12,FThe former TOWIE star, who shared the
OL,13,Fupdate on Instagram on Wednesday, said
OL,14,FPresley "landed face down on hard
OL,15,Fwooden floor" from about 3 metres high.
OL,17,F"My baby was struggling to breathe and
OL,18,Fthen passed out in our arms until
OL,19,Fcoming to in what like ages later,"
OL,20,Fshe wrote.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
