PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781139789
OL,3,CTOWIE star Jess Wright says son rushed
OL,4,Cto hospital after 'freak accident'
OL,6,FPresley was rushed to Royal London
OL,7,FHospital and treated in the trauma
OL,8,Funit, but he was discharged with no
OL,9,Finjuries.
OL,11,FWright shared a photo of Presley
OL,12,Fstrapped to a stretcher in the
OL,13,Fambulance while holding her hand.
OL,15,FWright said they had a "lucky escape"
OL,16,Fwith the accident and thanked
OL,17,Fparamedics and doctors for helping her
OL,18,Fson, who was in a "truly horrendous
OL,19,Fstate".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
