CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781139789
OL,3,CTOWIE star Jess Wright says son rushed
OL,4,Cto hospital after 'freak accident'
OL,6,FIn 2024, Presley was diagnosed with a
OL,7,Frare congenital heart disease, called
OL,8,Fbicuspid aortic valve, which Wright
OL,9,Fsaid has made her "very panicky" about
OL,10,Fhis safety.
OL,12,F"It was a freak accident that couldn't
OL,13,Fbe avoided, but I will say I'll be
OL,14,Fmore careful in future if the bouncy
OL,15,Fcastle is on a wooden floor," she
OL,16,Fwrote.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
