OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781139789
OL,3,CTOWIE star Jess Wright says son rushed
OL,4,Cto hospital after 'freak accident'
OL,6,FShe later shared a photo of him
OL,7,Fplaying a card game on his hospital
OL,8,Fbed, telling followers, "Five hours
OL,9,Flater and we were playing games,
OL,10,Fgrateful for his recovery!!!".
OL,12,FWright shares her son Presley with
OL,13,Fhusband William Lee-Kemp, who she
OL,14,Fmarried in 2021.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/4
